      "content": "Wait, why are you talking about wizards and forests? I just need actual flight advice. Can we just stick to the logistics? \n\nI'm specifically wondering about the hub options. If I go through Dubai (DXB) instead of Doha (DOH), which one is typically more efficient for a connection to Singapore when there are massive delays at Heathrow? I need to know which one has better transit times and less risk of further cancellations.",
